THE GAME
--------

  'Batonnade' is a Workbench game where the idea is to place bars
to create alignments of 8 sets of horizontal bars in the rows or 8
sets of vertical bars in the columns. Each set of bars from any
series must have one bar more or less than the number of bars on
either side in the series. The more bars there are in a series,
the higher the number of points you will get...

  As the game progresses, blocks will appear from time to time,
when there are 8 blocks on the game board, the game ends...

  Have fun!

